74
00:08:10,036 --> 00:08:11,959
- My horse couldn't make it.
- Mm.

75
00:08:12,076 --> 00:08:14,477
You don't know nothin'
'bout this filly here.

76
00:08:14,636 --> 00:08:16,047
Nope.

77
00:08:16,156 --> 00:08:18,442
