put a reward

557
00:31:48,628 --> 00:31:49,914
on the head of Major Marquis.

558
00:31:50,028 --> 00:31:51,792
- And I made them trees, Mannix.
- Get in!

559
00:31:51,908 --> 00:31:53,637
You best believe
I ain't looked back

560
00:31:53,748 --> 00:31:55,512
