didn't look kindly on.

605
00:33:31,939 --> 00:33:33,509
- Giddyup!
- Mannix's Marauders,

606
00:33:33,619 --> 00:33:35,269
- that's what.
- Get in! Hyah!

607
00:33:35,379 --> 00:33:37,461
And the fact that
Erskine Mannix's little boy

608
00:33:37,579 --> 00:33:39,467
would talk
about anybody else's behavior

609
