672
00:37:34,197 --> 00:37:36,677
All right, you two,
unhook the leaders.

673
00:37:36,797 --> 00:37:38,083
Come on, let's go.

674
00:37:38,197 --> 00:37:39,801
Open up!

675
00:37:39,917 --> 00:37:41,442
- You have to kick it open!
- Ya got to kick it open!

676
