Lucky devil.

714
00:39:27,027 --> 00:39:29,155
Jesus Christ, that's awful!

715
00:39:29,267 --> 00:39:31,793
Christ Almighty,

716
00:39:31,907 --> 00:39:34,910
what'd that Mexican fella do,
soak his old socks in a pot?

717
00:39:35,026 --> 00:39:37,632
Yes, uh... I-I think
