is traveling with you?

736
00:40:50,819 --> 00:40:52,150
Oh, he's lying.

737
00:40:52,259 --> 00:40:54,182
He ain't sheriff of nothin'.

738
00:40:54,299 --> 00:40:56,222
He's a Southern renegade.

739
00:40:56,379 --> 00:40:58,029
He's just talking hisself

