767
00:42:19,571 --> 00:42:21,175
I see.

768
00:42:22,811 --> 00:42:26,258
Uh, it says here
"dead or alive. "

769
00:42:26,371 --> 00:42:28,214
Yeah. It does.

770
00:42:28,331 --> 00:42:30,379
